vehicles.description: A blue sedan with roof signage indicating it could be a service vehicle, parked on the right side, in front of the ego vehicle.
vehicles.explanation: The positioning and status of the vehicle require caution, as the service vehicle might make unexpected movements, or the driver might return to the vehicle.

vehicles.description: A white truck parked on the right side perpendicular to the ego car's path
vehicles.explanation: The truck is obstructing the view of the road ahead and may also start moving without notice, so the ego car should be cautious and prepared to stop or evade.

other objects.description: Large industrial spools on the right-hand side and various items scattered around could indicate a working area or construction zone
other objects.explanation: The presence of these objects suggests a higher likelihood of sudden obstructions or the entry of workers and vehicles into the road which the ego car needs to be prepared for.

suggestions: The ego car should proceed with caution, being prepared to steer or lane-change to the left to avoid the blue sedan and white truck ahead, while maintaining awareness of potential other vehicles that may be navigating around the parked vehicles. Maintain a moderate speed to allow for timely reactions to any unseen hazards that may emerge from the industrial area.
